<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="264000000t" end="279430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">被推下来了</p>
<p begin="279430000t" end="293200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">为什么, 隼人…</p>
<p begin="308640000t" end="326560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">这不可能爬得上去</p>
<p begin="366610000t" end="376610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">会死</p>
<p begin="391210000t" end="405820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">我会死吧</p>
<p begin="441680000t" end="459620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">竟然还活着</p>
<p begin="472550000t" end="499230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">看来你是被同伴推下来的</p>
<p begin="510510000t" end="549700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">竟然跟关系那么险恶的人跑来爬这种高山</p>
<p begin="549700000t" end="569720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">愚蠢也该有个限度吧</p>
<p begin="596000000t" end="616430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">我在临死之际</p>
<p begin="616430000t" end="636460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">看见了白色的幻觉</p>
<p begin="733220000t" end="756580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="756580000t" end="784950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="784950000t" end="807460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="807460000t" end="835820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="835820000t" end="858340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="858340000t" end="886710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="886710000t" end="909240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="909240000t" end="937600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="937600000t" end="989720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="989720000t" end="1023930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="1023930000t" end="1063550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="1078990000t" end="1123190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="1123190000t" end="1177000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="1177000000t" end="1225390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="1225390000t" end="1254150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="1254150000t" end="1288360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="1359260000t" end="1379710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">我不知道为什么会被推下来</p>
<p begin="1384710000t" end="1403480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">他是值得信任的朋友</p>
<p begin="1403480000t" end="1435180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">受到这种对待还敢这么说啊</p>
<p begin="1447270000t" end="1462700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">你是什么东西</p>
<p begin="1462700000t" end="1492310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">如果是我临死前的幻想, 那也太恶劣了</p>
<p begin="1504410000t" end="1516930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">真是的</p>
<p begin="1516930000t" end="1546110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">亏我特地变化成你们熟悉的样子</p>
<p begin="1546110000t" end="1578240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">最近的人类连雪女都不知道了吗</p>
<p begin="1602420000t" end="1642050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不, 我还以为雪女应该会更美一点</p>
<p begin="1642050000t" end="1680010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">都油尽灯枯了还有力气说笑啊</p>
<p begin="1680010000t" end="1697940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我还有什么好在乎的</p>
<p begin="1697940000t" end="1721710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">反正这样下去迟早会被冻死</p>
<p begin="1728380000t" end="1750910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那就算变成被雪女杀死</p>
<p begin="1750910000t" end="1767170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">也没什么差别吧</p>
<p begin="1767170000t" end="1808890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">你就没想过要求我救你吗</p>
<p begin="1808890000t" end="1831820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">雪女是杀人的妖怪吧</p>
<p begin="1838070000t" end="1889790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你连小泉八云的《雪女》都没读过吗</p>
<p begin="1889790000t" end="1928590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">故事里的年轻男性可是被雪女救了喔</p>
<p begin="1934010000t" end="1969450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">我倒想问为什么雪女会看过小泉八云的书</p>
<p begin="1974470000t" end="2022010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">雪女有时会假装成人类混入村落</p>
<p begin="2022010000t" end="2054550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">小泉八云的书里也有写到这件事喔</p>
<p begin="2153810000t" end="2178830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">这样应该足够撑一晚了吧</p>
<p begin="2200520000t" end="2221800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">摔到这种地方的人</p>
<p begin="2221800000t" end="2247650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">天都还没黑就回到山脚的话</p>
<p begin="2247650000t" end="2266430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">想必也会引起骚动</p>
<p begin="2266430000t" end="2293540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">等明天傍晚再送你下山</p>
<p begin="2293540000t" end="2308120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你就休息一会儿吧</p>
<p begin="2313130000t" end="2330240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">为什么要救我</p>
<p begin="2343170000t" end="2357760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">这个嘛…</p>
<p begin="2357760000t" end="2383200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我瞧你年轻, 而且…</p>
<p begin="2400310000t" end="2415740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">挺俊俏的</p>
<p begin="2431160000t" end="2449530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">开玩笑的</p>
<p begin="2449530000t" end="2493310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">你虽然五官端正, 但表情凶恶了些</p>
<p begin="2493310000t" end="2506250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">眼神太凌厉啰</p>
<p begin="2512920000t" end="2534190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">你若是能平安下山的话</p>
<p begin="2534190000t" end="2552950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">好歹去读读小泉八云的书吧</p>
<p begin="2561290000t" end="2575480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">一有人遇难</p>
<p begin="2575480000t" end="2600930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">搜救作业就会把山里弄得很吵闹</p>
<p begin="2600930000t" end="2610930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">除此之外</p>
<p begin="2610930000t" end="2648890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">为了减少未来发生的事故还可能进行开发</p>
<p begin="2648890000t" end="2670570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">那我还不如救人就好了</p>
<p begin="2686850000t" end="2715210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">然后你身上有钱吗</p>
<p begin="2727710000t" end="2740230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">是有一些</p>
<p begin="2740230000t" end="2763580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">那么给我一半</p>
<p begin="2763580000t" end="2780690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">要是身上完全没钱</p>
<p begin="2780690000t" end="2798620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">就算下了山也会很困扰</p>
<p begin="2798620000t" end="2814880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我就不强求全额了</p>
<p begin="2820720000t" end="2841990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">拿这点代价换取性命很划算吧</p>
<p begin="2848260000t" end="2873270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">妖怪拿钱做什么</p>
<p begin="2873270000t" end="2912900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">最近人类制造的酒和食物都很好吃</p>
<p begin="2912900000t" end="2938750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">没有钱就买不了啦</p>
<p begin="2944180000t" end="2974630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">我虽然能不被察觉地偷偷拿走</p>
<p begin="2974630000t" end="2994230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">但万一害店家倒闭就不好了</p>
<p begin="3008820000t" end="3028430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">随意搅乱人类的世界</p>
<p begin="3028430000t" end="3051780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">之后只会害到自己</p>
<p begin="3051780000t" end="3073070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">这点规矩还是得遵守的</p>
<p begin="3078480000t" end="3109350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">趁这种机会拿点好处也没什么关系吧</p>
<p begin="3114350000t" end="3140210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">她明明是妖怪却这么正经</p>
<p begin="3144800000t" end="3184420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">你没考虑过杀了我拿走所有钱吗</p>
<p begin="3184420000t" end="3211120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">你比较希望我那么做?</p>
<p begin="3257420000t" end="3271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">当然是不想啦…</p>
<p begin="3271600000t" end="3321650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">那你是不是该为刚才说我不美道个歉呢</p>
<p begin="3327900000t" end="3349590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">可是故事里的雪女</p>
<p begin="3349590000t" end="3373770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">都更有魅力, 更有气质啊</p>
<p begin="3389630000t" end="3428840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">本想着你要是敢违心奉承就杀掉你的</p>
<p begin="3428840000t" end="3448020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">看来没那么简单就上当呢</p>
<p begin="3460120000t" end="3488480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">都到这地步了, 别设奇怪的陷阱啦</p>
<p begin="3488480000t" end="3505160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">开玩笑的</p>
<p begin="3505160000t" end="3524760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你可要好好活到明天喔</p>
<p begin="3529760000t" end="3563140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">要是擅自冻死了, 我也不会有罪恶感的</p>
<p begin="3618600000t" end="3634870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">不是幻觉?</p>
<p begin="3650720000t" end="3669080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我得救了吗</p>
<p begin="3826730000t" end="3843000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">还活着啊</p>
<p begin="3843000000t" end="3864270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">好痛…</p>
<p begin="3864270000t" end="3883870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">怎么了, 哪里痛</p>
<p begin="3883870000t" end="3897210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">全身都痛</p>
<p begin="3904730000t" end="3917230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">好</p>
<p begin="3917230000t" end="3932250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">那这样呢</p>
<p begin="3964370000t" end="3979800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">别掉下去啰</p>
<p begin="3979800000t" end="3991890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">准备下山吧</p>
<p begin="4149560000t" end="4163740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">真惊人</p>
<p begin="4163740000t" end="4182910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">虽然我想不需要特意提醒</p>
<p begin="4182910000t" end="4203770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">不过切记我的事情, 无论对双亲兄弟</p>
<p begin="4203770000t" end="4222130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">还是妻子都要保密</p>
<p begin="4222130000t" end="4245890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">要是胆敢透漏一句话</p>
<p begin="4245890000t" end="4273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">无论你在哪我都会去杀了你</p>
<p begin="4289700000t" end="4305550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">也就是说如果哪天我想寻死</p>
<p begin="4305550000t" end="4329320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">只要跟别人提及你就行了呢</p>
<p begin="4329320000t" end="4348500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">好不容易才得救</p>
<p begin="4348500000t" end="4367260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">别说那种丧气话行吗</p>
<p begin="4367260000t" end="4380190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">开玩笑的</p>
<p begin="4380190000t" end="4392710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">我会保守秘密的</p>
<p begin="4410230000t" end="4450260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">反正说被雪女救了也没人会相信吧</p>
<p begin="4475720000t" end="4491560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">昌幸在山顶附近的山脊</p>
<p begin="4491560000t" end="4508240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">头朝下摔了下去</p>
<p begin="4508240000t" end="4536610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">整个人埋进雪里就看不见了</p>
<p begin="4546200000t" end="4572900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">要是我有回去找他就好了</p>
<p begin="4572900000t" end="4593750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">你别责怪自己</p>
<p begin="4593750000t" end="4618770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">搜救队明天早上就会出动</p>
<p begin="4689680000t" end="4708870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">昌, 昌幸…</p>
<p begin="4708870000t" end="4731800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">你怎么还活着</p>
<p begin="4746390000t" end="4763090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">我是被他推下去的</p>
<p begin="4781850000t" end="4797690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">我本来以为要死了</p>
<p begin="4797690000t" end="4830640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">但奇迹似地发现下山路径就活下来了</p>
<p begin="4835650000t" end="4852760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">请逮捕他</p>
<p begin="4882780000t" end="4921990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">嫌犯似乎供称他是"着了魔"才犯案的</p>
<p begin="4934080000t" end="4964950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">因为喜欢的女性单恋你</p>
<p begin="4964950000t" end="4995810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">被女性拜托, 帮助她向你告白</p>
<p begin="5000810000t" end="5017090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">嫌犯虽然心怀忌妒</p>
<p begin="5017090000t" end="5048790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">但为了女性还是向你提及这件事</p>
<p begin="5063790000t" end="5077570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">你在说谁啊</p>
<p begin="5092570000t" end="5113430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你看似毫无兴趣的样子</p>
<p begin="5113430000t" end="5130950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">成了压垮他的最后一根稻草</p>
<p begin="5138030000t" end="5154310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">要是你死了</p>
<p begin="5154310000t" end="5181000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">趁女性难过时靠近的话</p>
<p begin="5181000000t" end="5210190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">自己说不定就有机可趁</p>
<p begin="5210190000t" end="5244810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">他说当时便突然这样想到</p>
<p begin="5264840000t" end="5284020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">真是无聊的理由</p>
<p begin="5288600000t" end="5330320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">竟然为了这点小事差点被高中死党谋杀</p>
<p begin="5330320000t" end="5346580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">真不敢相信</p>
<p begin="5346580000t" end="5395800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">不, 或许认为我们是朋友的只有我吧</p>
<p begin="5461690000t" end="5503830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">隼人的双亲希望你收下慰问金</p>
<p begin="5509240000t" end="5545110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">看那个样子, 他们大概会坚持到底吧</p>
<p begin="5560540000t" end="5577640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">对方相当富裕</p>
<p begin="5577640000t" end="5590150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">如果你想快点了结这件事</p>
<p begin="5590150000t" end="5617690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">最好还是接受吧</p>
<p begin="5617690000t" end="5649380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">我明白了, 诉讼的部分也麻烦您了</p>
<p begin="5655230000t" end="5686920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">我再见到隼人也只会尴尬而已</p>
<p begin="5686920000t" end="5706530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">希望不用见面就能结束这件事</p>
<p begin="5734470000t" end="5764500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">没想到世上竟然有这么可怕的事</p>
<p begin="5795780000t" end="5814130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">以后还是别再爬山了吧</p>
<p begin="5857100000t" end="5878360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">(十一年后)</p>
<p begin="6175750000t" end="6187010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">原来如此</p>
<p begin="6187010000t" end="6199510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">真是的</p>
<p begin="6199510000t" end="6230380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">亏我特地变化成你们熟悉的样子</p>
<p begin="6230380000t" end="6246240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">原来是这个意思啊</p>
<p begin="6311290000t" end="6338830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">我以前曾经差点死在山里</p>
<p begin="6344240000t" end="6376360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">当时遇到一个自认是美女的女人</p>
<p begin="6407220000t" end="6428500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">那个女人自称是雪女</p>
<p begin="6428500000t" end="6455610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">用妖怪的力量救了我</p>
<p begin="6537780000t" end="6580730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">(雪女的窘境)</p>
<p begin="6586580000t" end="6614090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">多亏有她, 我才能像这样活着</p>
<p begin="6614090000t" end="6643300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">不过我有时仍会疑惑</p>
<p begin="6643300000t" end="6662890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">那到底是不是一场梦呢</p>
<p begin="6685420000t" end="6700860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">给我等一下</p>
<p begin="6700860000t" end="6733390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我说过要是告诉别人就杀了你吧</p>
<p begin="6737980000t" end="6763410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我只是在跟当事人说说往事而已啊</p>
<p begin="6768840000t" end="6798450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">你还是没看小泉八云的书吗</p>
<p begin="6798450000t" end="6815140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">那里面登场的男人</p>
<p begin="6815140000t" end="6856430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">可是明知故犯惹怒了雪女喔</p>
<p begin="6856430000t" end="6867260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我看了</p>
<p begin="6871440000t" end="6889370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">那个男主角在说溜嘴时</p>
<p begin="6889370000t" end="6919810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">不知道妻子就是雪女本人</p>
<p begin="6919810000t" end="6969030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">但我很确定你就是当时的雪女才讲的</p>
<p begin="6969030000t" end="6989470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">所以不算泄露秘密</p>
<p begin="6989470000t" end="7017010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">你这应该是歪理吧</p>
<p begin="7021180000t" end="7031590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">算了</p>
<p begin="7031590000t" end="7067460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">不过你居然认得出我就是当时的雪女啊</p>
<p begin="7077060000t" end="7097080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">长相和雪白的肤色都没变</p>
<p begin="7097080000t" end="7110850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">怎么可能会看错呢</p>
<p begin="7150890000t" end="7170480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">看来天生丽质还是藏不住啊</p>
<p begin="7170480000t" end="7190510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">不用勉强自己说这种话吧</p>
<p begin="7190510000t" end="7226380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">信不信我现在就把你<br />扔到之前差点死掉的地方</p>
<p begin="7234310000t" end="7250140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">那样或许也不错呢</p>
<p begin="7263500000t" end="7285190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">倒是你怎么认得出我</p>
<p begin="7285190000t" end="7307700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">那之后已经过十几年了</p>
<p begin="7307700000t" end="7335660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">我的长相应该随着年纪变了不少才对</p>
<p begin="7341490000t" end="7378200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">我最近救过的人类只有你一个</p>
<p begin="7378200000t" end="7403640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">而且我们妖怪</p>
<p begin="7403640000t" end="7436580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">不是只靠外貌来辨别人类的</p>
<p begin="7436580000t" end="7473700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">每个人都有不会轻易改变的气息和颜色</p>
<p begin="7509570000t" end="7545030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">我一直很在意没有好好回报你的恩情</p>
<p begin="7545030000t" end="7575050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">出社会后能自由使用的金钱也增加了</p>
<p begin="7581730000t" end="7612590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">请你吃几十支霜淇淋都不成问题喔</p>
<p begin="7612590000t" end="7643880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">不需要那么多霜淇淋啦</p>
<p begin="7643880000t" end="7677670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">不过我最近取得的人类货币确实有限</p>
<p begin="7677670000t" end="7700590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">物价也在上涨</p>
<p begin="7700590000t" end="7732720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">走进人类的店家也让我满紧张的</p>
<p begin="7732720000t" end="7768590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">左一句点数卡右一句特惠日什么的</p>
<p begin="7768590000t" end="7786930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">人类的时历跟我又没关系</p>
<p begin="7786930000t" end="7801530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">实在弄不清这些事情</p>
<p begin="7801530000t" end="7814890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">要是跟你一起的话</p>
<p begin="7814890000t" end="7836150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">就能在店里悠闲地选商品</p>
<p begin="7836150000t" end="7852830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">也不需要烦恼那些了吧</p>
<p begin="7852830000t" end="7884530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">我从这个月开始住在这城镇的郊外</p>
<p begin="7890380000t" end="7921240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">你可以在那边不避人耳目地吃饭喔</p>
<p begin="7928320000t" end="7948760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">那你会煮饭吗</p>
<p begin="7948760000t" end="7976710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">有些东西还是现做的比较美味呢</p>
<p begin="7988390000t" end="8021760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我去年离婚后厨艺就进步了不少</p>
<p begin="8044700000t" end="8076810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">仔细一瞧你脸色挺差的呢</p>
<p begin="8076810000t" end="8094750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">我现在严重不信任人类</p>
<p begin="8101830000t" end="8131870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">原本很信任才结婚的妻子搞外遇</p>
<p begin="8131870000t" end="8151050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">还差点被谋财害命</p>
<p begin="8156050000t" end="8169810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">最后只能离婚</p>
<p begin="8176070000t" end="8194850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">这是去年六月发生的事</p>
<p begin="8194850000t" end="8223210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">再加上我大学毕业后开的公司</p>
<p begin="8223210000t" end="8245720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">三个月前被合伙人背叛</p>
<p begin="8245720000t" end="8267000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">遭到大公司并购</p>
<p begin="8273680000t" end="8298700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我身为社长当然没有容身之处</p>
<p begin="8298700000t" end="8322880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">被朋友妻子伙伴接连背叛</p>
<p begin="8322880000t" end="8336660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">还丢掉了工作</p>
<p begin="8336660000t" end="8356680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">搞得我现在完全无法信任别人</p>
<p begin="8366260000t" end="8392540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">能让我像这样毫不避讳地抱怨的</p>
<p begin="8392540000t" end="8415480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">也就只有妖怪了吧</p>
<p begin="8435090000t" end="8460100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">所以我把身家整顿了一番</p>
<p begin="8460100000t" end="8474710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">独自移居到这里来</p>
<p begin="8480960000t" end="8508900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">倒是没想过会在这里巧遇你就是了</p>
<p begin="8513920000t" end="8544770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">那你生活上也有困难吧</p>
<p begin="8544770000t" end="8565220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">我可不会找这种人敲竹杠</p>
<p begin="8565220000t" end="8591910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">你这妖怪还是一样很有分寸呢</p>
<p begin="8597320000t" end="8614020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">虽然没了社长的地位</p>
<p begin="8614020000t" end="8638210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">但是没动到我的个人资产啦</p>
<p begin="8645720000t" end="8674480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">还够我过上30年的清闲日子呢</p>
<p begin="8690330000t" end="8706190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">怎么不早说</p>
<p begin="8706190000t" end="8734550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">那你其实挺有福气的嘛</p>
<p begin="8734550000t" end="8769580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">说起来差点被谋杀两次还能活下来</p>
<p begin="8769580000t" end="8791280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">不就代表你运气其实很好吗</p>
<p begin="8791280000t" end="8820890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">有钱却无法信任人的男人</p>
<p begin="8820890000t" end="8860090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">在古早的故事里都是下场凄惨的坏人吧</p>
<p begin="8860090000t" end="8878020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">真是个可怜的家伙</p>
<p begin="8890960000t" end="8925570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">我想喝好酒, 也想吃吃看海产的鱼</p>
<p begin="8931820000t" end="8946840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">好好招待我的话</p>
<p begin="8946840000t" end="8969370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">倒是可以陪你聊聊喔</p>
<p begin="8969370000t" end="8989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">我接下来正要去超市</p>
<p begin="8994800000t" end="9021920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">想吃什么随你拿</p>
<p begin="9027350000t" end="9050700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">有想吃的料理我就做吧</p>
<p begin="9096580000t" end="9148300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">雪女养成在入夜后一周会来两三次的习惯</p>
<p begin="9160390000t" end="9197510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">昌幸, 今天也带我去超市吧</p>
<p begin="9215860000t" end="9247560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">我想自己挑选食材</p>
<p begin="9247560000t" end="9284270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">那我们出镇去大一点的购物中心吧</p>
<p begin="9284270000t" end="9321810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">太常一起在镇上出入很容易被记住</p>
<p begin="9350170000t" end="9362680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">车子啊</p>
<p begin="9362680000t" end="9378520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">真好, 我第一次搭呢</p>
<p begin="9680080000t" end="9708440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">日本酒果然还是吟酿最棒了</p>
<p begin="9708440000t" end="9719710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">虽然啤酒也很好喝</p>
<p begin="9719710000t" end="9735960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">不过我更喜欢发泡酒</p>
<p begin="9760150000t" end="9782680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">真的只要咖哩乌龙面就好了吗</p>
<p begin="9782680000t" end="9793110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">无所谓</p>
<p begin="9793110000t" end="9820220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">应该说我就是想吃咖哩乌龙面</p>
<p begin="9820220000t" end="9835650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">你还真好打发</p>
<p begin="9835650000t" end="9862350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">我又不懂食材的价格</p>
<p begin="9868180000t" end="9903640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">不过最好别穿这身和服吃吧</p>
<p begin="9903640000t" end="9928250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">穿白衣服吃咖哩乌龙面可是大忌</p>
<p begin="9933660000t" end="9948260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">说什么呢</p>
<p begin="9948260000t" end="9972030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">讲到雪女就该是这打扮吧</p>
<p begin="10019170000t" end="10030010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">好好吃</p>
<p begin="10030010000t" end="10058370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">跟淋在米饭上的酱汁感觉又不一样呢</p>
<p begin="10058370000t" end="10082150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">那衣服为什么不会脏啊…</p>
<p begin="10092160000t" end="10102160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">(四个月后)</p>
<p begin="10102160000t" end="10111760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">现在?</p>
<p begin="10111760000t" end="10128450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我一个人在家</p>
<p begin="10128450000t" end="10148040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">最近还是都窝在家里</p>
<p begin="10148040000t" end="10159720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">这样啊</p>
<p begin="10164320000t" end="10195590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">我打算一边小酌一边看书到天亮</p>
<p begin="10201010000t" end="10212690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">社长</p>
<p begin="10212690000t" end="10228120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">我已经不是社长了</p>
<p begin="10232720000t" end="10244800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">失礼了</p>
<p begin="10253560000t" end="10265250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">室井先生</p>
<p begin="10265250000t" end="10273170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">怎么了</p>
<p begin="10278170000t" end="10315290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">我会等你开始新事业的</p>
<p begin="10330310000t" end="10342400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">那我要挂电话了</p>
<p begin="10342400000t" end="10357010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">之后的事就拜托你了</p>
<p begin="10357010000t" end="10374920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">好的, 再见</p>
<p begin="10412480000t" end="10440410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">刚炸好的热度真是太棒了</p>
<p begin="10446250000t" end="10473770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">比起天妇罗酱汁还是沾盐比较棒</p>
<p begin="10473770000t" end="10496730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">你身为雪女竟然觉得热的好…</p>
<p begin="10505480000t" end="10517170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">在古早的故事里</p>
<p begin="10517170000t" end="10550950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">还有碰到火炉的火或热茶就融化的例子耶</p>
<p begin="10555960000t" end="10574310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">你的身体都没事吗</p>
<p begin="10574310000t" end="10594320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">那是什么年代的话题啊</p>
<p begin="10594320000t" end="10605170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">要是会因为那点小事死掉</p>
<p begin="10605170000t" end="10628530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">雪女根本活不过一年吧</p>
<p begin="10635190000t" end="10683570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">人类明明就流传并相信<br />雪女会跟人产下后代的故事</p>
<p begin="10683570000t" end="10707360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">最好是会因为区区天妇罗就融化啦</p>
<p begin="10712360000t" end="10727790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">我有件事想问你</p>
<p begin="10734040000t" end="10755740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">会不会只是大部分的人类没察觉</p>
<p begin="10755740000t" end="10792860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">其实有很多像你这样的妖怪<br />混在人类社会之中?</p>
<p begin="10797870000t" end="10812880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">应该有吧</p>
<p begin="10812880000t" end="10850000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">不过跟人类扯上关系容易引来麻烦</p>
<p begin="10850000000t" end="10872510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">所以大概没有多少妖怪愿意</p>
<p begin="10877520000t" end="10909630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">怪异本身不见得比人类强大</p>
<p begin="10909630000t" end="10937170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">两方别扯上关系才能保持和平</p>
<p begin="10942180000t" end="10980120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">人类总是不懂得尊重和畏惧世界的伦理</p>
<p begin="10980120000t" end="10993880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">真是挺伤脑筋的</p>
<p begin="11003480000t" end="11049360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">那你老是跑来找我不会有问题吗</p>
<p begin="11049360000t" end="11090660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">同伴里也有妖怪劝我别这么做</p>
<p begin="11090660000t" end="11101500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">不过也有同伴觉得</p>
<p begin="11101500000t" end="11143200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">这样可以更了解人类所以没关系</p>
<p begin="11166560000t" end="11201600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">我也有担心自己会不会太过利用你</p>
<p begin="11201600000t" end="11225780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">去找公主殿下谘询过呢</p>
<p begin="11225780000t" end="11238720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">公主殿下?</p>
<p begin="11238720000t" end="11248320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">没错</p>
<p begin="11248320000t" end="11272910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">是我们这些被称为妖怪, 精怪</p>
<p begin="11272910000t" end="11309620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">幽灵, 魔物等存在的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="11318380000t" end="11344230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">我们之间也会产生纠纷</p>
<p begin="11344230000t" end="11378850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">有时也会碰上不知如何解决的问题</p>
<p begin="11378850000t" end="11398050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">有时则因人类的行为而困扰</p>
<p begin="11398050000t" end="11420150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">想要寻求帮助</p>
<p begin="11426820000t" end="11461030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">这种时候我们就会去拜托公主殿下</p>
<p begin="11476040000t" end="11499400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">我只见过她两次</p>
<p begin="11499400000t" end="11528170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">但是她的活跃表现聪明绝顶</p>
<p begin="11528170000t" end="11544030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">实在是太让人着迷了</p>
<p begin="11544030000t" end="11567380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">被妖怪供为神明的对象</p>
<p begin="11567380000t" end="11589060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">难道是很特殊的怪物吗</p>
<p begin="11589060000t" end="11620760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">不, 公主殿下是人类喔</p>
<p begin="11646630000t" end="11669140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">殿下立于人类与妖怪之间</p>
<p begin="11669140000t" end="11704600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">肩负维护世界伦理的职责</p>
<p begin="11710860000t" end="11737970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">公主殿下并没有舍弃身为人类的立场</p>
<p begin="11737970000t" end="11779250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">还为了我们从人类成为神</p>
<p begin="11790940000t" end="11808870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">那么, 那位公主殿下</p>
<p begin="11808870000t" end="11832220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">是怎么评断我们的关系的?</p>
<p begin="11832220000t" end="11847240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">她说只要不引起他人注意</p>
<p begin="11847240000t" end="11893540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">并注意不要被那个对象利用过头就没问题</p>
<p begin="11898130000t" end="11919400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">虽然让人类尝点甜头是无妨</p>
<p begin="11919400000t" end="11933170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">但不能用我们的力量</p>
<p begin="11933170000t" end="11967370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">对人类社会造成太大的影响</p>
<p begin="11967370000t" end="11981960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">说得很正确</p>
<p begin="11981960000t" end="12003650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">公主殿下还挺明事理的嘛</p>
<p begin="12003650000t" end="12047860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">她还说要是事情变麻烦的话<br />就冻死你快点脱身</p>
<p begin="12047860000t" end="12082070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">这个解决方案也太粗暴了吧, 公主殿下</p>
<p begin="12116260000t" end="12149620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">话说回来, 你跟邻里的关系如何啊</p>
<p begin="12154220000t" end="12165890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">因为我是个整天窝在家里</p>
<p begin="12165890000t" end="12185920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">又长得很可怕的外人</p>
<p begin="12185920000t" end="12207190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">附近的居民都很怕我</p>
<p begin="12207190000t" end="12219700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">进而回避</p>
<p begin="12219700000t" end="12241810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">好像还认为我是不是做黑的呢</p>
<p begin="12258480000t" end="12272670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">要是没有你的话</p>
<p begin="12272670000t" end="12288520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">我说不定会因为完全没跟人见面</p>
<p begin="12288520000t" end="12314380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">甚至忘记怎么发出声音呢</p>
<p begin="12314380000t" end="12329800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">太夸张了吧</p>
<p begin="12329800000t" end="12356510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">刚才不就有人打电话给你吗</p>
<p begin="12364840000t" end="12394030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">只是以前的下属来报告些杂事罢了</p>
<p begin="12394030000t" end="12425310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">对方很惋惜你无处发挥才能吧</p>
<p begin="12425310000t" end="12448260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">是啊, 但也只有她一个</p>
<p begin="12448260000t" end="12462020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">就算只有一个人</p>
<p begin="12462020000t" end="12484130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">当你要东山再起时也能成为助力的</p>
<p begin="12484130000t" end="12522910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">而且你看起来比之前有精神多了啊</p>
<p begin="12522910000t" end="12547520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">到你重新振作为止</p>
<p begin="12547520000t" end="12567550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">要我陪你多久都可以就是了</p>
<p begin="12580480000t" end="12625100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">毕竟我吃了很多美食还挺满足的</p>
<p begin="12635530000t" end="12660130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">这样我是不是占了太多好处啊</p>
<p begin="12666400000t" end="12678480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">对了</p>
<p begin="12678480000t" end="12708520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">你跟前妻分手已经很久了吧</p>
<p begin="12713100000t" end="12741460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">不介意的话, 我也可以当床伴喔</p>
<p begin="12773580000t" end="12803620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">你们妖怪的贞操观念有没有问题啊</p>
<p begin="12803620000t" end="12826980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">而且连这种事都要依赖你的话</p>
<p begin="12826980000t" end="12846150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">我也太丢脸了</p>
<p begin="12852840000t" end="12883270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">俗话说送到嘴边的肉哪有不吃的道理</p>
<p begin="12883270000t" end="12907470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">还是你比较喜欢翘臀</p>
<p begin="12907470000t" end="12935000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">多少让我保持点颜面吧</p>
<p begin="12940000000t" end="12961690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">现在的我跟死人没什么两样</p>
<p begin="12961690000t" end="12981710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">不是配得上你的人</p>
<p begin="12988380000t" end="13033840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">而且公主殿下也不会允许那种关系吧</p>
<p begin="13033840000t" end="13062620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">她说只要好好避孕就没关系呢</p>
<p begin="13082650000t" end="13112680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">那个公主殿下果然不能信任</p>
<p begin="13168150000t" end="13197340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">是刚才订的鳗鱼饭送来了吗</p>
<p begin="13210680000t" end="13234460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">昌幸, 我来帮你看着炉火</p>
<p begin="13234460000t" end="13248650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">快点去应门</p>
<p begin="13248650000t" end="13271590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">万一送货的走掉怎么办</p>
<p begin="13289100000t" end="13297860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">来了来了</p>
<p begin="13321630000t" end="13342900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">你是室井昌幸先生吧</p>
<p begin="13342900000t" end="13350410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">是</p>
<p begin="13385450000t" end="13402120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">你知道原田美春小姐…</p>
<p begin="13402120000t" end="13445090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">你去年离婚的前妻被杀害了吗</p>
<p begin="13503070000t" end="13529330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">那是新的委托者吗</p>
<p begin="13529330000t" end="13550610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">它只负责联络</p>
<p begin="13550610000t" end="13587730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">委托者是住在某座山上的雪女</p>
<p begin="13587730000t" end="13601070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">雪女?</p>
<p begin="13605250000t" end="13623180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">名为原田美春的女性</p>
<p begin="13623180000t" end="13668230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">在9月12日晚间遭到重殴死亡</p>
<p begin="13668230000t" end="13697010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">但新闻网站上也写得不是很清楚</p>
<p begin="13697010000t" end="13714110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">能查到的资料很少</p>
<p begin="13714110000t" end="13754140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">那么雪女为什么会跟杀人案件扯上关系?</p>
<p begin="13754140000t" end="13795860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">警方扣留了一个很有力的嫌疑犯</p>
<p begin="13795860000t" end="13826720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">但雪女说这个人在事件发生时</p>
<p begin="13826720000t" end="13847990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">有不在场证明, 并不是犯人</p>
<p begin="13847990000t" end="13873440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">所以希望我能帮帮他</p>
<p begin="13873440000t" end="13903880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">有不在场证明还被当有力嫌疑犯?</p>
<p begin="13910130000t" end="13941010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">毕竟证人就是这个雪女</p>
<p begin="13941010000t" end="13965190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">没办法跟警察说啊</p>
<p begin="13986460000t" end="14011480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">还没好吗, 昌幸</p>
<p begin="14011480000t" end="14041110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">再煎下去要焦了耶</p>
<p begin="14073210000t" end="14084060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">昌幸…</p>
<p begin="14154130000t" end="14167890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">怎么了吗</p>
<p begin="14172490000t" end="14184580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">没事</p>
<p begin="14215020000t" end="14227110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">你有养兔子啊</p>
<p begin="14270490000t" end="14300530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">(待续)</p>
